entry.title: How to go Module
entry.summary: It's easy to encounter some issues in your dependency management. Go module is a dependencies management tool of golang. Go mod is treated as default dependency management tool from go 1.13. And more and more golang developer start to use the Go module to manage their Go project. Based on this, it's necessary to study how to use go mod and how go mod works.
